These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
Hobby: skydiving, cooking, rock-climbing, sudoku
1. Hobby:cooking is between Hobby:rock-climbing and Hobby:sudoku##2
2. Hobby:cooking is on the left of Hobby:rock-climbing##1
3. Hobby:skydiving is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku | cooking | rock-climbing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
